p.e:
Anyland is a VR MMO all about creating 
worlds. If you can think it, you can make
 it! Limited only by your imagination, you 
can create worlds, [pause] tools, 
[pause] even your very own avatar! 
Anyland’s in-game modeling system lets 
you make any 3D object you want in no 
time at all. Fill virtual worlds with all 
your own creations, and explore them 
with friends. Entering its 6th year, 
Anyland’s community of everyone from 
sports fans to artists to programmers 
have filled its universe with endless 
worlds to visit and enjoy. 
Anyland is available free on Steam today; 
 join us as we create a universe together!

REMEMBER, ENJOY YOURSELF
AND JUST BE NATURAL!
